Changelog

Initial Release

Version 1.0

With ID Resistor you can easily identify SMD resistors and traditional through hole technology resistors, by entering the code printed on the resistor. You can enter the value of the resistor and get the corresponding code.

  • THT color code with 4 or 5 rings.
  • SMD resistor codes with 3 or 4 digits.
  • Support for dark mode.
